<P>
<B>Latest news;</B><BR>
<FONT color="red">19th March 99:</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">The account suspension period has been increased from 30
days to 90 days. This means that they will now only suspend your account
after 90 days of inactivity instead of the previous 30 days. Effective
from the 15th March 1999.</FONT>

<!-- END NAVNEWS -->
