<P>The latest news (I'm trying to keep this site as up to date as
possible) will always appear in the border on the left. Also keep an
eye on the news pages for previous important announcements.</P>

<P><FONT COLOR="RED">Please Note:</FONT> Due to other commitments, I
can't really update this site any further for the forseeable future.
Although, most of what you need to know to get your Amiga online to
Freeserve is here. If you do want more info, please visit the sites
listed on the links page.</P>

