<HR COLOR="BLACK">
<SMALL><FONT COLOR="RED">Please note:</FONT> I have <B>nothing</B> to do with
freeserve, Dixons, Currys, etc., I have only provided this information
to help Amiga owners connect to Freeserve. I would strongly recommend
that you keep your existing internet account and use this one as a
backup or for extra webspace (or whatever), as, being a free service, it
may not be as good as a &quot;paid for&quot; ISP. They will also
terminate your account if you do not log in for 90 days (and there have
also been reports of accounts being deleted by accident...).</SMALL>


